Membership Opportunities
Click to Download Membership Application
Become A Member At Indianwood!
Whether you have been golfing your entire life, or have just begun to appreciate the game,
Indianwood Golf Course
offers a membership option that suits you. Our challenging course and friendly staff ensures our members will enjoy bringing guests out for a drink, as well as perfecting their game.
We encourage you to request a tour of our facility, and welcome any questions you may have. For additional information about pricing and our application process, please call us at 772-597-3794 or send an email to admin@indianwoodgolfclub.com. We look forward to hearing from you.
*rates are subject to 6.5% Florida sales tax
MEMBERS MUST ALSO PURCHASE AN ANNUAL TRAIL FEE (RESIDENTS USING THEIR OWN CART) OR ANNUAL CART PASS (MEMBERS USING THE CLUB’S CARTS)
Taxes not included. Prices subject to change. See General Manager for complete terms & conditions.
Email: admin@indianwoodgolfclub.com
Membership Opportunities

EVENT BOOKING
We strive to ensure that your events are memorable and enjoyable.
Contact Us for your wedding hosting, anniversary/retirement or birthday parties, corporate events, fundraising / charity events abd golf tournaments.
Our banquet areas are available for both private and corporate events. From the moment your guests drive up to our beautiful and spacious 5,000 square-foot clubhouse, they will revel in the lovely golf course surroundings.
If you have questions or would like to book and event at our club;
Contact our Event Hosting Department at
admin@indianwoodgolfclub.com
or Phone:  (772) 597-3794
